{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"301515abf3","title":"讽刺诗——“肃反干部颂”","origin":"《右派言论选辑》（社会主义教育参考资料之一，内部材料　仅供参考，沈阳师范学院社会主义教育办公室 1958．3）","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fa66f7a1ca","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"301515abf3"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7eb95ac9a4","name":"沈阳师范学院"},{"id":"c74a30c055","name":"李慎徽"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c84f1c47f1","type":"title","text":"讽刺诗——“肃反干部颂”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"f46f582f5c","type":"authors","text":"沈阳师范学院李慎徽","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"d893aabd49","type":"subtitle","text":"（李慎徽：沈阳师范学院中文系学生)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"6f3dd09dea","type":"paragraph","text":"“肃反干部，功大无边，损人利己，不断升官。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"403e6133e6","type":"paragraph","text":"踥蹀躜营，居然又作了党员，今后自然是永垂不朽，流芳万年。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"42bfd7fd96","type":"paragraph","text":"“在肃反中间，他们胡作非为，无法无天。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"4848924756","type":"paragraph","text":"名利冲昏了头脑，使他们倒行逆施，肆无忌惮。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"3d0089e964","type":"paragraph","text":"以莫须有的罪名把我辈严加惩办，在言行的束缚上，不下于监狱的囚犯。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"99769028c3","type":"paragraph","text":"在精神上，更受到了非人道的摧残。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"4cf7271453","type":"paragraph","text":"我辈为他们付出的牺牲，真是绝后空前，","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"697c8743d5","type":"paragraph","text":"我们流了多少血泪，","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"1c57e42f97","type":"paragraph","text":"三好的勋章才挂到了他们的胸前。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"0dfa0af9ae","type":"paragraph","text":"我们用肉体堆砌了进升之阶，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"99c9f41399","type":"paragraph","text":"这才使他们一步登了天。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"7e792e49bc","type":"paragraph","text":"………………","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"0ffcd6a556","type":"paragraph","text":"当时我辈岂敢争辩，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"de5d18ce29","type":"paragraph","text":"因为他们掌握死生之权。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"28d196be1f","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反结束，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"bb81aa5075","type":"paragraph","text":"我辈仍然未曾见天。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"24a63517f0","type":"paragraph","text":"忍恨吞声，有口难言，","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"8a60b8e230","type":"paragraph","text":"他们大权在握，而且有组织作为靠山。”","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"dd94323234","type":"paragraph","text":"另一首诗：","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"c3c3718d6c","type":"paragraph","text":"“假若对他们的错误还继续宽容，","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"5a39bf69a6","type":"paragraph","text":"今后还有什么真理可言。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"ad23ad71d1","type":"paragraph","text":"今天我辈要当仁不让，大胆呐喊：","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"6ff5879e37","type":"paragraph","text":"为了今后正义的伸张，","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"0c748262d3","type":"paragraph","text":"为了维护大学生的尊严，","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"981c546173","type":"paragraph","text":"坚决揭露他们的丑恶面目，","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"be8d954b45","type":"paragraph","text":"使他们感到以后作假的困难，","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"5250adc3fb","type":"paragraph","text":"拿出肃反干部，严加惩办。”","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"d17746edbb","type":"paragraph","text":"另一首诗肯定“胡统领剿匪记”：","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"45f8fbf3dc","type":"paragraph","text":"伟大共产党，","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"c0f502844f","type":"paragraph","text":"功德实难铭。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"df14e57c0f","type":"paragraph","text":"然有坏党员，","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"d2ebd4b411","type":"paragraph","text":"谁也不否认。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"e11eae0704","type":"paragraph","text":"君如不相信，","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"ccc0d8a9f2","type":"paragraph","text":"请看今日的胡统领。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"cc31fb51ea","type":"paragraph","text":"残民以自肥，","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"dc4cd707e2","type":"paragraph","text":"统领的本性，","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"8d0ed2b9ef","type":"paragraph","text":"损人以利己，","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"9db6428e66","type":"paragraph","text":"酷吏的良心。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"c1735b35f0","type":"paragraph","text":"两者若相比，","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"c01865f153","type":"paragraph","text":"一丘之貉云。","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"8888ded814","type":"paragraph","text":"“歌颂”官吏们，","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"9625261e59","type":"paragraph","text":"谁曰不近情。","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"84fa0a8353","type":"paragraph","text":"党与胡统领，","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"e2da5905e6","type":"paragraph","text":"怎能一体论。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"738649749f","type":"paragraph","text":"劝君深思虑，","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"},{"id":"84984c2a1a","type":"paragraph","text":"头脑要清醒。","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3"}],"page":{"id":"f5db79ea0d","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"301515abf3","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}